  }
}
```

#### Luma Image Model (Async/Polling)
**File:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775496855969-0s377s/packages/luma/src/luma-image-model.ts`

**Key characteristics:**
- Implements polling pattern for async generation
